Membership Fee for 2025 Golf Season.
Single 12 Month Membership Rates
$2910 ($2310+ tax. $600 food minimum**)
includes unlimited greens fees, handicap, 10% off soft goods in golf shops, 10% off restaurant including alcohol sales.
$600
will be applied to the restaurant as a credit.
*This can be paid monthly and does not include golf cart.
** the restaurant is not currently open. this is a guide to what we expect members to spend in the restaurant once open. those not willing to participate will be changed to a multi play card option.
